  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Basic Education for the children of slum-dwellers</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The rural poor and unskilled workers migrate to the city in search of livelihood, as the employment in the unskilled sector is high.  But due to the costly city life and higher rentals, these poor people form into groups and build make shift houses in the suburbs or open places which finally become slum areas due to the unorganised, unplanned occupation and living. These poor migrants who live a hand to mouth life by earning very little on daily labour and miserable living conditions make them.</narrative>
  </description>
